docs {
  # List Resources
  
  List all approved resources with optional filtering, search, and pagination.
  
  ## Query Parameters
  
  - `limit` (optional): Number of results per page (1-100, default: 20)
  - `offset` (optional): Pagination offset (default: 0)
  - `category_id` (optional): Filter by category UUID
  - `tag_ids` (optional): Filter by tag UUIDs (comma-separated)
  - `search` (optional): Full-text search query
  - `type` (optional): Filter by resource type (pdf, youtube, markdown)
  - `sort` (optional): Sort order (newest, oldest)
}
